			<h3 ><a href="#p160645">Re: To (probably) discuss a lot of basics</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=160645&amp;sid=ccca31e45dd7a790da195e88f9dcfb63#p160645"><img src="http://thejapanesepage.com/phpbb/styles/tjp-embed/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=26732&amp;sid=ccca31e45dd7a790da195e88f9dcfb63">furrykef</a></strong> &raquo; Mon 11.09.2009 4:01 pm </p>

			

